  "title": "Full-Time Bread Baker",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Woodlands, Buona Vista, Dhoby Ghaut & Hougang </strong><br />⏰ 7am-4pm/ 7.30am-4.30pm <em><strong>(OT may be required based on production needs)</strong></em><br />📅 6-days work week<br />💰 Gross salary up to $3,200/month <em><strong>(Salary commensurate based on experience)</strong></em><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u><br />• Prepare, proof, bake and finish a wide variety of breads according to company's recipes and standards.<br />• Handle and identify multiple types of doughs, ensuring correct usage of different bread varieties. <br />• Follow daily production schedules to meet outlet sales demand.<br />• Load, operate and monitor ovens ― must accurately judge baking times and temperatures for different products to achieve perfect colors, crust and internal doneness. <br />• Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of workstations, equipment and storage areas. <br />• Follow food safety hygiene and workplace safety guidelines at all times.<br />• Assist with stock control, including proper storage and rotation of frozen dough and ingredients. <br />• Work closely with outlet staff to ensure timely product availability on shelves. <br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u><br />• Proven experience in bread baking <em><strong>(commercial/ retail bakery experience preferred)</strong></em>. <br />• Physically fit and able to stand for long hours, lift trays, and work in a warm kitchen environment. <br />• Able to work early morning shifts, weekends and public holidays. <br />• Reliable, responsible and able to work independently with minimal supervision. <br />• Team-player with a positive work attitude. <br />• Able to work in a fast-paced environment and meet daily production targets. <br /></p><p><u><strong>Staffs' Benefits:</strong></u><br />• Annual & Medical leaves entitlement <br />• Medical claims<br />• AWS/ VB<br />• Annual salary increment <strong>(based on individuals' work performance)</strong><br />• Attendance, weekend & public holiday shift allowances<br />• OT payable<br /></p><p>📱 Interested applicants, can <strong>WhatsApp @ 84944246 </strong>OR<strong> Tele: @fourleaveshr</strong></p>",
